&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a data-goodreads-type=&#34;book&#34; data-goodreads-id=&#34;13888&#34; href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13888.knife-of-dreams&#34;&gt;Knife of Dreams&lt;/a&gt;, in which things begin moving again as the world begins the march to the Last Battle.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
